Pendulum Effect
 You cannot Pendulum Summon monsters, except "Yang Zing" or "Sephira" monsters. This effect cannot be negated.

 Monster Effect
 If this card is Special Summoned from the Deck or is Pendulum Summoned: You can target 1 "Yang Zing" or "Sephira" monster you control, except "Sephira Fuxi, Treasure of the Yang Zing"; this turn, it is treated as a Tuner monster. If you activated this effect, place this card on the bottom of the Deck when it leaves the field. You can only use this effect of "Sephira Fuxi, Treasure of the Yang Zing" once per turn.
